summary: This is Lisa, a beautiful female Nord.
descriptionHtml:
This is my first file uploaded to the Nexus sites!

This is Lisa, a beautiful female Nord.
I decided to go into the keep with Ralof but it\'s up to you to decide weather or not you want to side with the Imperials or Stormcloaks. Also just wanted to note that none of the armor in the screenshots are made by me.

To install just place the file in My Documents > My Games > Skyrim > Saves
If you want to edit her just type showracemenu in console.
Please Endorse if you like her! :)

v1.1 - Just wanted to fix her nose a bit and make it shorter length.
